          "_name": "header08",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"header8\" group=\"Headers\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen}\" plugins=\"formstyler, datepicker\">\n\t<mbr-parameters>\n\t\t<header>Size</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n\t\t<header>Show/Hide</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n\t\t<header>Background</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"color\" name=\"bgColor\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#edefeb\" selected>\n\t\t<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"usedRecaptcha\" value=\"false\">\n\t</mbr-parameters>\n\n\t<div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n\t<div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row content-wrapper justify-content-center\">\n\t\t\t<div mbr-form class=\"col-lg-7 mbr-form\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text-wrapper align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<form action=\"vasyukovevgeny@gmail.com\" name=\"Form Name\" method=\"POST\" class=\"mbr-form form-with-styler\" data-verified=\"vasyukovevgeny@gmail.com\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"dragArea row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Индивидуальные уроки по бизнес- и системному анализу</b></h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tПомогу освоить профессию с нуля, систематизировать опыт или подготовиться к собеседованию. Занятия онлайн в удобном для вас темпе.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div data-for=\"email\" class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"test@email.ru\" data-form-field=\"email\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"form-control\" value>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-auto mbr-section-btn\" mbr-buttons=\"true\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrLink,-mbrBtnRemove,-mbrBtnAdd\"><a type=\"submit\" class=\"w-100 btn btn-success\" data-app-placeholder=\"Введите Текст\">Записаться на пробный урок</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div hidden=\"hidden\" data-form-alert class=\"alert alert-success col-12\">Спасибо за заполнение формы!</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div hidden=\"hidden\" data-form-alert-danger class=\"alert alert-danger col-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tOops...! some problem!\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</form>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-lg-5 col-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/airbrush-image-enhancer-1773493846289-1773493846289-1036x1054.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</section>",
